      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782155454199,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Here, we can't keep two different vectors of Files & Folders\nso instead we keep one vector, but then it will be of what?\nHence we create common parent abstract class for both\nFiles & Folders",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Here, we can't keep two different vectors of Files & Folders\nso instead we keep one vector, but then it will be of what?\nHence we create common parent abstract class for both Files & Folders",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "EDz4VHRkDJl7eI6jN7BQ-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 528.5432906781255,
